2:14:16.080 --> 2:14:19.040
 nanny in your head that, how do I look?

2:14:19.040 --> 2:14:20.080
 Do people like me?

2:14:20.080 --> 2:14:21.080
 How do I look?

2:14:21.080 --> 2:14:22.080
 How's my hair?

2:14:22.080 --> 2:14:23.080
 Do people like me?

2:14:23.080 --> 2:14:24.080
 Should I have said that?

2:14:24.080 --> 2:14:25.240
 That all goes away.

2:14:25.240 --> 2:14:26.240
 You're free from that.

2:14:26.240 --> 2:14:30.840
 You're free from the most sadistic, superego self critic you could possibly have, at least

2:14:30.840 --> 2:14:32.160
 for a while.

2:14:32.160 --> 2:14:34.320
 The world is vivid.

2:14:34.320 --> 2:14:35.960
 It's super salient to you.

2:14:35.960 --> 2:14:39.720
 There's an ongoing sense of discovery.

2:14:39.720 --> 2:14:47.300
 Although often you know you're exerting a lot of metabolic effort, it feels effortless.

2:14:47.300 --> 2:14:53.160
 So in the flow state when you're sparring, your hand just goes up for the block and your

2:14:53.160 --> 2:14:56.200
